      "topic": "html",
      "sender": "Engineer",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>春节促销 - LYF香瓜子葵花子组合装</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #D0021B;\n            --secondary-color: #F5A623;\n            --light-color: #F4F4F5;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--light-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header, section, footer, nav {\n            padding: 20px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: auto;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h1 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n\n        .product-specs {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .price-box {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .price-box h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n\n        .promotion-tags {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .promotion-tags span {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .purchase-channel {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .purchase-channel button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .purchase-channel input {\n            width: 60px;\n            padding: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .cart-management {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .category-nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .category-nav li {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 8px 15px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .coupon-area {\n            background-color: #fff5e6;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .reviews {\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #222;\n            color: #ccc;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .price-box {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n\n            .purchase-channel {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: flex-start;\n            }\n\n            .category-nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\" id=\"hero-section\">\n        <h1>春节促销：LYF香瓜子葵花子组合装</h1>\n        <p>欢庆佳节，限时优惠，香瓜子与葵花子美味齐享！</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"product-specs\" id=\"product-specs\">\n        <h2>产品规格</h2>\n        <p>精选原料、地道口味，香瓜子醇香回甘，葵花子香脆可口，满足您的节日零食需求。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"price-box\" id=\"price-box\">\n        <h3>现价：¥29.9 原价：¥39.9</h3>\n        <p>立省¥10，限时优惠进行中</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"promotion-tags\" id=\"promotion-tags\">\n        <span>倒计时：02:15:23</span>\n        <span>库存紧张</span>\n        <span>热销爆款</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"purchase-channel\" id=\"purchase-channel\">\n        <button>立即购买</button>\n        <input type=\"number\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\">\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cart-management\" id=\"cart-management\">\n        <h2>购物车</h2>\n        <p>查看已选商品，调整数量，轻松结算。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <nav class=\"category-nav\" id=\"category-nav\">\n        <ul>\n            <li>坚果炒货</li>\n            <li>糖果巧克力</li>\n            <li>饼干糕点</li>\n            <li>饮料冲调</li>\n            <li>休闲零食</li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"coupon-area\" id=\"coupon-area\">\n        <h3>优惠券</h3>\n        <p>点击领取，享受更多节日专属优惠。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"reviews\" id=\"reviews\">\n        <h3>用户好评</h3>\n        <p>众多买家晒图好评，味道赞不绝口。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"footer\">\n        <p>LYF食品官方旗舰店</p>\n        <p>售后服务：400-123-4567 | 邮箱：service@lyf.com</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
